code: function Timer(nowDate){var openDate=new Date('2022/02/22 00:00:00');var nowDate=Object.values(nowDate)[0];var diffTime=openDate.getTime()-nowDate.getTime();var timerDays=(diffTime-diffTime%(1000*60*60*24))/(1000*60*60*24);var timerHours=(diffTime%(1000*60*60*24)-diffTime%(1000*60*60*24)%(1000*60*60))/(1000*60*60);var timerMinutes=(diffTime%(1000*60*60*24)%(1000*60*60)-diffTime%(1000*60*60*24)%(1000*60*60)%(1000*60))/(1000*60);var timerSeconds=(diffTime%(1000*60)-diffTime%(1000*60)%1000)/1000;return timerDays+" : "+timerHours+" : "+timerMinutes+" : "+timerSeconds;}export default Timer;
